M: Did you like it?
W: Well, it has an interesting story, but I don’t 
like the ending.
M: Me neither. The director wrapped up the story 
too abruptly.
W: I still don’t understand why the main character
acts that way.    
M: Yeah. That’s why I bought and read the book 
afterwards.
W: Did that help you understand the ending of the  
movie?
